title: Mountain Lake Ecosystem
description: A vibrant illustration of a mountain lake ecosystem featuring a serene lake surrounded by towering mountains and dense forests. Various wildlife is depicted, including a bear and her cubs, a moose drinking from the lake, and a bird soaring above. The foreground showcases diverse flora, including colorful flowers and mushrooms. Inset circles highlight microscopic organisms and plants, emphasizing the ecosystem's complexity.
